    "Background": {
      "text": "A\ncongenital heart defect\nin which the left heart is severely underdeveloped\nAccounts for 2 to 3% of all\ncongenital heart disease\n[1]",
      "subsections": {
        "Physiology": {
          "text": "With a diminutive LV, the RV must perfuse both pulmonary and systemic circulations\nSurvival is dependent on:\nPDA\n(for systemic perfusion from RV to the aorta)\nNonrestrictive\nASD\nto ensure adequate mixing of oxygenated and deoxygenated blood",
          "tables": []
        }
